<section class="case_study_content Milton CAT">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-8 large-centered columns">
      <h2>Getting the Message to Busy Supervisors More Efficiently</h2>
      <p>
        For David Convery, Corporate Manager of Environmental, Safety, and Health at Milton CAT, marketing a weekly safety message is key to their injury reduction efforts. Supervisors are some of the busiest people in any organization and keeping them informed and engaged is always challenging. David was looking for a way to effectively communicate safety information with Supervisors.  H.Engage gave him a way to do that.
      </p>

      <h2>Just Another Email</h2>
      <p>In addition to posters, monthly trainings, and Safety Briefs, a lot of information gets sent out on a weekly basis via email. The documents had great content; however the key points were easily overlooked. A marketing tool was needed that could not only save time but would communicate the message.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============= small sample tiles ============= -->
  <div class="row study_samples editorial_divider">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
      <p class="editorial_title">Sample Milton CAT tiles</p>
    </div>
    <div class="large-12 columns">

      <div class="tile_thumbnail asha_fitness"><div class="tile-wrapper">
        <div class="tile_thumbnail_image">
          <%= image_tag "case_studies/asha_tile_fitness.png", "alt" => "Last Chance to Sign Up for this Session of Fitness Classes" %>
        </div>
        <div class="headline">
          <span class="text">Last Chance to Sign Up for this Session of Fitness Classes</span>
        </div>
      </div></div>

      <div class="tile_thumbnail asha_team"><div class="tile-wrapper">
        <div class="tile_thumbnail_image">
          <%= image_tag "case_studies/asha_tile_team.png", "alt" => "Speech-Language Pathology Cluster, Team Highlight" %>
        </div>
